WEBVTT

00:01:57.767 --> 00:02:02.207
because she is not only marrying
the boy but the entire family.

00:02:03.527 --> 00:02:09.743
Girls are taught repeatedly
to adjust and compromise.

00:02:09.767 --> 00:02:16.583
They are taught that the needs of others
must always be kept before their own.

00:02:16.607 --> 00:02:23.607
That is why they know how to be
sensitive to other's emotions.

00:02:25.767 --> 00:02:28.737
This ability is not seen in boys

00:02:28.737 --> 00:02:33.847
because it is hardly touched
upon in their upbringing.